a","tid":1564892,"uid":43500,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"嗰啲早幾日未升前<br />\n不停話會停牌 唔聽佢哋講嗰啲人 收嗲啦<br />\n我哋賺錢嗰陣又唔知你哋喺邊度<br />\n依加先入返嚟潤鳩人 黑心人通常冇運行<br />\n<br />\n其他戰友 唔好再因爲連登仔話有利好因素就追<br />\n要了解情況不樂觀 大家今次真係因爲貪心先會咁<br />\n雖然你哋話跳樓可能係講笑<br />\n但都想講千祈唔好睇唔開 錢可以賺得返<br />\n亦都唔好借錢追啦 我見到好似有人話借錯allin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家都平到手離場 輸少當贏 <br />\n中秋快樂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d98a539a8f0d053b8f299d061e5f21782fa225","tid":1564892,"uid":131522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12e5edf7ee4f73c1c5e1aae3fab60906c7b79a04","tid":1564892,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43184caea3429df8c8cf09ac3baa078584bd86c7","tid":1564892,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b044afd8acdec40eb9ada4555e04d8f9e17a8b87","tid":1564892,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"老散聚集地<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"呢度哀聲處處<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"上個post都見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf6a3043f17083ee0affe49e921983deccce6e3","tid":1564892,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02d98a539a8f0d053b8f299d061e5f21782fa225","tid":1564892,"uid":131522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12e5edf7ee4f73c1c5e1aae3fab60906c7b79a04","tid":1564892,"uid":141630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43184caea3429df8c8cf09ac3baa078584bd86c7","tid":1564892,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"呢